node.contents: I am developing an Android app and faced the same problem. I use Eclipse as well. My problem was that someone had disabled the app from our test phone because it was still buggy, so I had to go to Settings->Apps->MyApp->Enable. That fixed it for me.

astNode.text: I am developing an Android app and faced the same problem. I use Eclipse as well. My problem was that someone had disabled the app from our test phone because it was still buggy, so I had to go to Settings->Apps->MyApp->Enable. That fixed it for me.
